OL,3,CDriving bans and bank account snooping
OL,4,Cpowers planned for benefit fraudsters
OL,6,FBenefit cheats could be banned from
OL,7,Fdriving if they repeatedly fail to pay
OL,8,Fback cash to the taxpayer, under a new
OL,9,FGovernment drive to curb welfare fraud.
OL,11,FThe Department for Work and Pensions
OL,12,F(DWP) will also be able to recover
OL,13,Fmoney directly from fraudsters' bank
OL,14,Faccounts, in what has been dubbed the
OL,15,Fbiggest fraud crackdown in a
OL,16,Fgeneration.
OL,18,FThe Public Authorities (Fraud, Error
OL,19,Fand Recovery) Bill, which would put
OL,20,Fthe measures into law, is due to be
OL,21,Fintroduced in Parliament on Wednesday.
