OL,6,FShe added: "This means greater
OL,7,Fconsequences for fraudsters who cheat
OL,8,Fand evade the system, including as a
OL,9,Flast resort in the most serious cases
OL,10,Fremoving their driving licence. Backed
OL,11,Fup by new and important safeguards
OL,12,Fincluding reporting mechanisms and
OL,13,Findependent oversight to ensure the
OL,14,Fpowers are used proportionately and
OL,15,Fsafely.
