OL,6,FThey also plan to introduce new
OL,7,Foversight and reporting mechanisms to
OL,8,Fmonitor how the powers are used.
OL,10,FElsewhere in the Bill, the Public
OL,11,FSector Fraud Authority will be given
OL,12,Fmore powers to tackle Covid-era fraud.
OL,14,FHelen Whately, the shadow work and
OL,15,Fpensions secretary, welcomed the
OL,16,Fmeasures, and claimed they were a
OL,17,F"continuation" of the Conservatives'
OL,18,Fwork in power.
